entry.title: NMAT 2022 Registration, Eligibility, Syllabus, Dates @nmat.org.in
entry.summary: NMAT Registration 2022: Graduate Management Admission Council (GMAC) has started the NMAT 2022 registration window on August 1st, 2022. The NMAT registration 2022 can be done on the NMAT official website, register.nmat.org. Candidates interested in pursuing MBA can appear for NMAT by GMAC exam 2022 after filling the NMAT 2022 application form.
